casebody.data:
Vacated and Remanded on Appeal

No. 74-1327. Democratic Executive Committee of Columbiana County, Ohio, et al. v. Brown, Secretary of State of Ohio.

Appeal from D. C. N. D. Ohio. Judgment vacated and case remanded so that a fresh order or decree may be entered from which a timely appeal may be taken to the United States Court of Appeals *1003for the Sixth Circuit. MTM, Inc. v. Baxley, 420 U. S. 799 (1975).
